author: Caleb Quinley
title: Thais left stranded overseas slam coronavirus policy confusion
description: 'Fit-to-fly' rules leave Thai students, professionals, struggling to get home amid confusion over repatriation flights.
content: Bangkok, Thailand - When Chayanan "Ann" Meesomboonpoonsuk, 23, left Thailand to study in the Netherlands in June, she never imagined that in a time of global crisis, her own country would block her from being able to return home. Ann was in the Czech Republic… [+5378 chars]
